markets.title: Will the US agree to a new Iranian nuclear deal this year?
markets.rules_primary: If Iran agreed to, signed, or accepted safeguards agreement with the International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA) to allow them to monitor Iran's Nuclear program before Jan 1, 2026, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: An agreement also made with other countries (i.e. multilaterally) is still encompassed if Iran participates. safeguards agreement with the International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA) to allow them to monitor Iran's Nuclear program
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
